<!doctype html>
<html>
<head>
    <title>disc|zump - Home</title>
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css?family=Orbitron:400,900" rel="stylesheet" type="text/css">
    <link href='https://fonts.googleapis.com/css?family=Play' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css'>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/static/css/home.css">
</head>
<body>
    <div class="dz-nav">
      <a href="/" id="dz-nav-logo"><img src="/static/logo/logo_text.svg" class="nav-logo"></a>
      <div class="navbar-btn-container full-height float-right">
          <div class="navbar-btn-list">
              <a href="/login"><span class="nav-btn">Sign In</span></a>
              <a href="/signup"><span class="nav-btn">Sign Up</span></a>
          </div>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div id="main-background" {{#if reqScroll}}style="background-attachment: scroll !important;"{{/if}}>
      <div class="link-container" id="main-links">
        <span class="scroll-icon"><i class="fa fa-arrow-circle-down"></i></span>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="section-define" id="section-disczump">
        <div class="define-content">
            <div class="define-icon left"></div>
            <div class="define-main">
                <div>
                    <div class="define-word">
                        discâ€¢zump <span class="word-small">[disk zump'], n.</span>
                    </div>
                    <div class="define-description">
                        A social disc golf inventory network enabling users to organize, 
                        maintain and share collections across any internet-enabled device.
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
    <div class="section-info" id="section-inventory">
      <div id="inventory-carousel" class="carousel slide">
        <div class="carousel-inner" role="listbox">
          <div class="item active">
            <div class="carousel-title">
              <div>Intuitive Interface</div>
            </div>
            <div class="carousel-item" id="carousel-interface">
              <div class="carousel-content">
                <div class="content-container">
                  <p>
                    An inventory website should be easy-to-use and provide a 
                    way to view all items in a clear and concise manner. The purpose
                    of an inventory is to <i><b>organize</b></i>, afterall.
                  </p>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="item">
            <div class="carousel-title">
              <div>Sleek Views</div>
            </div>
            <div class="carousel-item" id="carousel-views">
              <div class="carousel-content">
                <div class="content-container">
                  <p>
                    We all know how good it feels to see your collection right
                    there in front of you, in all of it's glory. Or maybe you are the 
                    one who loves graphical representations <i>(*cough* <b>nerd</b> *cough*)</i>. 
                    Either way, we have a view for you.
                  </p>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="item">
            <div class="carousel-title">
              <div>Adaptive Features</div>
            </div>
            <div class="carousel-item" id="carousel-features">
              <div class="carousel-content">
                <div class="content-container">
                  <p>
                    The <i>best</i> inventory site will grow
                    with your collection, providing those great features such as 
                    quick filters, sorting, color representations and custom 
                    statistics. 
                  </p>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="item">
            <div class="carousel-title">
              <div>Connect And Share</div>
            </div>
            <div class="carousel-item" id="carousel-share">
              <div class="carousel-content">
                <div class="content-container">
                  <p>
                    It's the 21st century, which means SHARE EVERYTHING! But really,
                    what is the point of having an awesome collection if you can't 
                    show it off. Connect via Facebook and share your discs with the 
                    world.
                  </p>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="carousel-controller">
          <ol class="dz-carousel-indicators no-select">
            <span data-target="#inventory-carousel" data-slide-to="0"><i class="fa fa-circle"></i></span>
            <span data-target="#inventory-carousel" data-slide-to="1"><i class="fa fa-circle-o"></i></span>
            <span data-target="#inventory-carousel" data-slide-to="2"><i class="fa fa-circle-o"></i></span>
            <span data-target="#inventory-carousel" data-slide-to="3"><i class="fa fa-circle-o"></i></span>
            <span class="carousel-action"><i class="fa fa-pause"></i></span>
          </ol>
        </div>
        <a class="carousel-direction left" href="#inventory-carousel" role="button" data-slide="prev">
          <span class="arrow"><i class="fa fa-arrow-circle-left" aria-hidden="true"></i></span>
          <span class="sr-only">Previous</span>
        </a>
        <a class="carousel-direction right" href="#inventory-carousel" role="button" data-slide="next">
          <span class="arrow"><i class="fa fa-arrow-circle-right" aria-hidden="true"></i></span>
          <span class="sr-only">Next</span>
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="section-define anti">
        <div class="define-content">
            <div class="define-icon left"></div>
            <div class="define-main">
                <div>
                    <div class="define-word">
                        zump <span class="word-small">[zump']</span>
                    </div>
                    <div class="define-description">
                        <ol>
                          <li><span class="desc-type">noun.</span> A collection.</li>
                          <li><span class="desc-type">verb.</span> The act of using disc|zump to organize and 
                          share your disc golf collection.</li>
                        </ol>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
    <div class="section-info wpad" id="section-platform">
      <div class="section-title">
        Cross-Platform Design
      </div>
      <div class="section-inner">
        <div class="section-graphic section-icons">
          <i class="fa fa-desktop"></i>
          <i class="fa fa-laptop"></i>
          <i class="fa fa-tablet"></i>
          <i class="fa fa-mobile"></i>
        </div>
        <div class="section-details">
          disc|zump is <a href="http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Responsive_web_design" target="_blank">responsive</a> by nature, allowing users to manage and share
          their inventory from any internet-enabled device.
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="section-info wpad" id="section-beta">
      <div class="section-title">
        We're In Beta!
      </div>
      <div class="section-inner">
        <div class="section-graphic">
          <img class="logo-block" src="/static/logo/logo_small_beta.svg">
        </div>
        <div class="section-details">
          We have been working hard to build a <b>highly-functional</b> and <b>feature-rich</b> disc 
          golf inventory website. Now, we need people like yourself to dive in 
          and become one of the first to use disc|zump. Create an account and begin 
          to build your collection. Keep it private or share your discs directly to 
          Facebook, and don't forget to give us feedback from your account dropdown menu!
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="section-info" id="section-footer">
      <div class="footer-bar">
        <span class="footer-links"><a href="mailto:ben@disczump.com">Contact Us</a></span>
        <span>Copyright <i class="fa fa-copyright"></i> disc|zump, LLC.</span>
      </div>
    </div>
    <script src="/static/js/validation.js"></script>
    <script src="/static/js/home.js"></script>
</body>
</html>